Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:50.33,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}腳下的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.92,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,521)}今天也一如往常
