Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:04.47,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}弄髒的襯衫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.43,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}沾染上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:10.39,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}這自欺欺人的謊言…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:15.52,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,348)}我到底在保護什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.94,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}不畏失去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:23.65,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}即便長大成人 也心懷夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.66,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}因為我只希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.16,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}自己能將這些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:31.08,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8\fad(0,351)}視為驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.12,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}吐出來 捨棄掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.00,op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1235,360)\blur8}見到你
